      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 9.8,
      "text": "It is currently a cloudy morning in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 27 degrees Celsius."
    },
    {
      "end": 19.98,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 17.04,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "adef89dd539",
        "aca4fa5e6a3"
      ],
      "end": 40.89,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 20.28,
      "text": "Competition in frontier AI is shifting toward high-fidelity sensory output and physical integration. MiniMax has released Speech 2.8 to create more lifelike AI vocalizations. At the same time, Tesla continues engineering work on the gear systems for its Optimus humanoid robot."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "ab6a0c04b02",
        "aedf79de14d"
      ],
      "end": 63.39,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 41.21,
      "text": "This push for embodied and sensory AI is mirrored by a drive toward agentic productivity tools in China. Alibaba Cloud is promoting MuleRun as part of a new AI workforce productivity suite. Kuaishou's Kling AI platform is also expanding its capabilities as a creative production tool for high-end video and image generation."
    },
    {
      "end": 66.63,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 64.63,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 74.99,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 69.93,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain cloudy with rain chances up to 83 percent and temperatures between 24 and 30 degrees Celsius."
    },
    {
      "end": 78.87,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 74.99,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 87.884,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 79.41,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 89.81,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 87.884,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
